  "version_pin_rationale": "libwayland 1.20.0 is the jammy security-pocket build (all three .debs share a version). client0 is what Wayland clients (foot terminal, waybar) link against; server0 is what the compositor (Hyprland) links against; egl1 is what Mesa's EGL backend links against to integrate the compositor's surface with EGL contexts. Hyprland 0.50 needs >= 1.20; jammy's 1.20.0 just clears the floor."
